preparation.p:
By using 3,5-dicyanobenzyl bromide synthesized by the method described in 
          
            Journal of Organic Chemistry 55(3) 1040-1043 (1990
          ) instead of 3-trifluoromethylbenzyl bromide, reactions and treatments were performed in the same manner as those of Example 1 to obtain the title compound as pale yellow oil.
